node.text: India and the world are in crisis. Now is the time to come together and support each other in all ways. Some of this is physical, some mental, and some soulful. Join us at @dancewithmadhuri & stay #UnitedByDance during these difficult times. It's our humble initiative to spread positivity, happiness, and wellness through dance. There are free classes, live sessions & much more in store to engage your mind, body, and soul from the sanctity of your homes. So enroll today on dancewithmadhuri.com/unitedbydance.php (Link in bio)
